# Loophacka

React + TypeScript SPA built with Vite. Client-side only — no backend in this repo.

## Commands

```bash
npm install      # setup
npm run dev      # http://localhost:5173
npm run build    # typecheck + production build
npm run lint     # oxlint
npm run preview  # preview production build
```

Run `npm run build` after non-trivial changes.

## Structure

- `src/main.tsx` — entry point
- `src/components/` — shared UI (create as needed)
- `src/hooks/` — custom hooks (create as needed)
- `src/assets/` — imported static assets
- `public/` — static files at root paths (e.g. `/icons.svg`)

## Agent behavior

- Minimize scope; only change what the task requires
- Match existing style: single quotes, no semicolons on imports
- Do not add npm dependencies unless required or asked
- Do not commit or push unless explicitly requested
- Do not create markdown docs unless requested
